<p>We get a huge error!</p>
<p>Once we've moved the code, we don't have access to the PDO object anymore.
So how can we get it?</p>
<h2 id="accessing-external-objects-from-a-service">Accessing External Objects from a Service <a class="headerlink" href="services#accessing-external-objects-from-a-service" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
